title: Fight'N Rage Update 4
description: DescriptionFight Rage is a brand new old-school side-scroller beatm up. Inspired by the classics from the olden age, and with an art style that mimics the aesthetic from the 90's arcade gems, this game pays homage to all classic gameplay features that makes this genre one of the best from its time!DetailsGenre: Classic 2D side-scroller beatm up / brawler.Number of players: From one up to three players local co-op.Available languages: English and Spanish.FeaturesA lot of Combinations
